- Praise Helix and head outside of Mt. Moon.

## Route 4

- Talk to the Karate Man on the right and teach Mega Kick over Withdraw (Slot 4).
- If you have no Cut slave, catch a Sandshrew / Rattata in the grass (Tackle to weaken).
  - Can teach Strength to Sandshrew later if caught.
  - If you die using a Rare Candy will revive Wartortle.
- Head to Cerulean City.

## Cerulean City

- Grab this hidden Rare Candy. ![Rare Candy](images/frlg/CeruleanRareCandy.png)
- Open your bag
  - Use 2x Potion.
  - Rare Candy to level 20.
    {% rare-candy id="cerulean-rare-candy-1" /%}
    {% rare-candy id="cerulean-rare-candy-2" /%}
  - Teach Bite over Bubble.
- Head to the gym.
- Skip both gym trainers and talk to Misty from the right side.

### Leader Misty

{% trainer-encounter trainerId="TRAINER_LEADER_MISTY" %}
{% strategy %}
Bite (x2)
{% /strategy %}
{% calcs %}
{% ko-chance move="Bite" hits=2 /%}
{% /calcs %}
{% /trainer-encounter %}

{% trainer-encounter trainerId="TRAINER_LEADER_MISTY" slot=1 %}
{% strategy %}
Bite, (Tackle), Bite
{% /strategy %}
- Tackle if low roll on the first Bite.
{% calcs %}
{% damage-in move="Swift" /%}
{% damage-in move="Water Pulse" /%}
{% /calcs %}
{% /trainer-encounter %}

- After the fight:
  - Teach Water Pulse over Tackle (Slot 2).
  - Heal for Rival so you can survive a Quick Attack and Vine Whip.
  {% calcs-for trainerId="TRAINER_RIVAL_CERULEAN_BULBASAUR" %}
  {% damage-in move="Quick Attack" /%}
  {% /calcs-for %}
  {% calcs-for trainerId="TRAINER_RIVAL_CERULEAN_BULBASAUR" slot=3 %}
  {% damage-in move="Vine Whip" /%}
  {% /calcs-for %}

