## Vermilion City

- Press Select to teach Cut to Rattata / Sandshrew.
- Cut the bush and enter the gym.
- Save after you find the first switch of the puzzle.
  - The second switch can be located to any adjacent can.
  - Soft reset if you did not get the second switch after saving. ![Can Order](images/frlg/VermillionGymCans.png)

### Gentlemen Tucker

{% trainer-encounter trainerId="TRAINER_GENTLEMAN_TUCKER" %}
{% strategy %}
Water Pulse
{% /strategy %}
{% calcs %}
{% speed-check /%}
{% /calcs %}
